{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f5ed36c976","title":"复彭德怀等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a41787ee0d","index":0,"year":1949,"month":8,"day":22,"articleId":"f5ed36c976"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"dcd5ee4e83","type":"title","text":"复彭德怀等电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"f5ed36c976"},{"id":"ecbd260ca6","type":"paragraph","text":"十九兵团何时尚宁夏进军，待占领兰州后看情况决定。如果王震四个军确有把握占领青海，则十九兵团可在兰州休息十天或半月后即向宁夏，否则可略为推识。入新疆部队至少休整一个月，必要时韵量增加休整时间，好作充分准备。入川部队待与贺面商后作最后决定，大体上以十八兵团入川是适宜的。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"f5ed36c976"},{"id":"aa749cd7d4","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]这是毛泽东复彭德怀并告贺龙、习仲勋电的主要内容。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"f5ed36c976"}],"page":{"id":"d7ab9a70ca","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"f5ed36c976","start":157,"end":157}}}},"__N_SSG":true}